{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Welcome to Topac Battles</strong>, an idle game like no other, where magical and cozy monsters await your discovery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/1.gif?t=1728991620\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect 18 Monsters across 7 rarities!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Feed and evolve Monsters up to Gen 3!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn money through Monster battles or sales!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Purchase 3 new Topac type with your earnings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Access 4 unique Topac, each offering different rarities!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enhance your battle lineup to 6 hexagons!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Push your limits with unlimited battles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Expand your park's capacity to 100!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Capture increasingly rare Monsters after battles!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Name your Monsters and park!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Monsters hunt and feed while offline; return to see their progress!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Buy more parks and switch between them!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Create a feeding frenzy to grow your Monster!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/FeedingFrenzy.gif?t=1728991620\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unlock rare Monsters through with Topacs!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2839420/extras/TopacReveal.gif?t=1728991620\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;With 18 Topac Mons